systemModel

Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • systemModel.Move

  • public class Move
extends java.lang.Object
    A Move object describes the motion of one tile (or two tiles in the case of a merge move) in the game.
    Author:
    Sayantani Ghosh, Piyush Mantri, Dinesh Papineni
